This SlackBuild will build a package containing the firmware required
to run a FacetimeHD webcam. This is principly used when building the
bcwc-pcie driver.

The homepage for this project is
https://github.com/patjak/facetimehd-firmware

However, since no releases are available, this has been forked to
produce a release at
https://github.com/kdtsh/facetimehd-firmware/